            "provider": "copilot-opus46",
            "locale": "en",
            "hint": "'But' expresses an unexpected or paradoxical contrast between two qualities of the same person or thing.\nThe adjectives `small` and `strong` carry opposite physical connotations — small size is not expected to come with great strength.",
